Subject: [PATCH 06/20] Oprofile: add omap2plus platform pmu mode support

Add oprofile pmu mode support for comcerto platform.

Signed-off-by: Guoqing Jiang <Guoqing.Jiang@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/kernel/pmu.c |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/kernel/pmu.c b/arch/arm/kernel/pmu.c
index a124312..10a6d66 100644
--- a/arch/arm/kernel/pmu.c
+++ b/arch/arm/kernel/pmu.c
@@ -27,7 +27,7 @@
  * second goes to cpu 1 etc.
  */
 static const int irqs[] = {
-#if defined(CONFIG_ARCH_OMAP2)
+#if defined(CONFIG_ARCH_OMAP2) || defined(CONFIG_ARCH_OMAP2PLUS)
 	3,
 #elif defined(CONFIG_ARCH_BCMRING)
 	IRQ_PMUIRQ,
